      "title": "<p>As you know, fixing federal hiring has been at the top of my wishlist for a long time. I had the chance to talk about this on OddLots with the amazing Tracy Alloway and Joe Weisenthal, and it's out today. We cover some other stuff too. :) <br><a href=\"https://bloom.bg/3Cfti9V\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>https://</span><span>bloom.bg/3Cfti9V</span><span></span></a></p>",
